<heading>jobs list - Show active flows.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  jobs list
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Lists all active flows in the current session.
The current foreground flow is marked with an arrow.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
fg, bg, stop, man
</paragraph>
